---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Course" description="Course information for Ngawi Golf Club — a links course on the Wairarapa Coast.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-green-900 mb-4">The Course</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-10">
      Ngawi Golf Club offers a unique links experience on the remote southern tip of the Wairarapa Coast.
      With wild winds off Cook Strait and panoramic sea views, every round is memorable.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-900 mb-4">Course Details</h2>
        <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-green-100 pb-2">
            <dt class="text-gray-600">Holes</dt>
            <dd class="font-medium">9</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-green-100 pb-2">
            <dt class="text-gray-600">Par</dt>
            <dd class="font-medium">36</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-green-100 pb-2">
            <dt class="text-gray-600">Type</dt>
            <dd class="font-medium">Links</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-green-100 pb-2">
            <dt class="text-gray-600">Location</dt>
            <dd class="font-medium">Ngawi, Wairarapa</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between">
            <dt class="text-gray-600">Green Fees</dt>
            <dd class="font-medium">$10 NZD</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-900 mb-4">Facilities</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span> Clubhouse with basic amenities</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span> Practice putting green</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span> Equipment available on request</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span> Visitors welcome</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span> Pay-and-play, no booking required</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Getting Here</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
        Ngawi is located at the southern tip of the Wairarapa, approximately 2.5 hours from Wellington via Martinborough and Palliser Bay.
        Follow State Highway 53 through Lake Ferry — Ngawi is at the end of the road, right on the coast.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
